9:57.000Z","msg":"一至兩次"},{"pid":"40ce83fc636dcf9e8f7a573dcfbe0f85472875d2","tid":585572,"uid":28845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"每對情侶既既相處方式都唔同，舒服就得啦。<br />\n就好似我同女朋友咁，大家都好忙，有時一個禮拜都見唔到一次，但係點都好我地會日日臨瞓傾一陣電話同對方講聲good night<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f3d0682e82fc2e22d9df38a26b6efa1ee991bb","tid":585572,"uid":143307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:17:05.000Z","msg":"一開始 天天見 總是膩在一起 <br />\n尾聲時 她變得很難約<br />\n<br />\n感覺就是一個人很愛你的話<br />\n會想盡辦法增加相處時間吧<br />\n<br />\n已成ex 她也有了新歡很久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06b145bb57d7f81e1bf5e3b4bddb4efd077a7aa","tid":585572,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d1551430f2c9b77c9a3a454f7300e3e24ec2765","tid":585572,"uid":3929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"5年都係日日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ae2940b00706a1bcde214be45b005be44d4880","tid":585572,"uid":2786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"一個月見十幾次走唔甩"},{"pid":"b2ec598b218893f1c65be5455ad3a7fbf635c6c7","tid":585572,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7467204ed3d4ac19cc572ff694491587db148128","tid":585572,"uid":133420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:53:41.000Z","msg":"1個星期要見佢3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最大問題係出完街要去佢屋企住<br />\n我返緊學 佢返緊工<br />\n平時返學已經放得晏<br />\n最大問題係我有時想做下自己想做既野<br />\n係佢屋企好似無曬空間 私隱咁<br />\n同佢一齊之後機乎無乜點同朋友出過去<br />\n其實我好想放假同朋友聚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想開口同佢講 可能平時放學見下 <br />\n唔洗每個星期去佢屋企訓<br />\n就話成日係到住2，3日驚佢屋企人唔鍾意<br />\n佢又覺得無問題"},{"pid":"32bc1a3774efea128c4f8422260f3dfa1742d617","tid":585572,"uid":214536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"我個個一星期最少要四次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}